    <div class="column">
      <h1 class="title">ICT training</h1>
      <div class="content">
        The IT fundamentals course sharpens our clientsâ€™ ability on concept of ICT using computer and managing files as well as using the web and communication technologies. Upon successful completion of this course the  candidates have to pass tests in the following areas:
