      <div class="column is-5">
      <%= image_tag "communication_training.jpeg", class: "medium-image"  %>
      </div>
      <div class="column">
        <h1 class="title">Networking</h1>
        <div class="content">
          Brief history of cellular wireless telephony, network architectures, Radio technologies, available services and various interfaces will be presented.  Topics will include GSM, GPRS, EDGE, UMTS, HSPDA, HSPA, LTE, LTE-A. The specification, strength and weaknesses of each of these technologies will be highlighted, their architecture, call flows and differences indicated. Introduction to modulation schemes used in cellular communication including TDMA, FDMA, TDD, FDD, OFDM, CDMA. Learn the definition of cell in regard to cellular communication.
        </div>
      </div>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column">
          <h1 class="title">E-learning</h1>
          <div class="content">
            Hypertech also trains on modern instructional methods such as e-Learning Pedagogy. This course equips teachers with modern instructional skills that would enable them teach courses offered online. This course is especially useful for college lecturers, and university lecturers as well as organizations that would wish to offer online courses.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-5">
        <%= image_tag "e-learning.jpeg", class: "medium-image"  %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-5">
        <%= image_tag "fiber_optics.jpeg", class: "medium-image"  %>
        </div>
