          <h1 class="title">Fiber optics</h1>
          <div class="content">
            Fundamentals of optical fiber communication system will be introduced. Topics for this training will include; Introduction & principles of fiber optics, fiber classification, cable types, fiber design and systems, installation, fiber splicing, connectors and Termination, fiber testing, Fiber standards, enclosures and panels, test equipments; restoration and maintenance; System design and component issues, application, Fiber optic safety.
          </div>
